reviews.text: Rarely have dinner here because of the staffs were so unfriendly except asking for extra tips. I just have been there 2 days ago since 2016. By the way, the food were just reached the standard line so couldn't get any special tastes. It would be better if they upgraded their service and provided cleaning cups, bowls, plates and chopsticks.
